<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>FAQ</div><div><br /></div><div># How to check what version of Debian I am running?</div><div>=&gt; lsb_realese -a </div><div><br /></div><div># No “ifconfig” found:</div><div>=&gt; sudo apt-get install -y net-tools</div><div><br /></div><div># I don’t want to use the CD/DVD</div><div>=&gt; sudo vi /etc/apt/sources.list # Disable the CD</div><div><br /></div><div># How do I autologin to the KDE 5 Plasma ?</div><div>=&gt; su </div><div>=&gt; sddm --example-config &gt; /etc/sddm.conf</div><div><br /></div><div># Edit the "sddm.conf” file</div><div>[Autologin]</div><div>User=khasanov</div><div>Session=plasma.desktop</div><div><br /></div><div># How do I make shortcuts in the KConsole”</div><div>“Settings" -&gt; “Configure Shortcuts…”</div><div>( Note: If you are using the Apple keyboard, the CMD might not work)</div><div> <en-media hash="ef4f119afea616a34deb24b5a256c90d" type="image/png" /></div><div>   <en-media hash="ca5e1d0b8c2795b9e2012bd429d7e3a2" type="image/png" /></div><div><br /></div></en-note>